						<summary>

						<p>Threshold of the shrine of the goddess in the temple of Chennakēśava.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription may be assigned on the basis of palaeography to the 15th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>Built in. It seems to record a gift made to god Chennakēśava by Sāḷuvarāya. It refers to some community which might be Dommari.</p>						

						</summary>
